data.description: Looking for maintenance free living- this is the home for you! Beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath townhome with an open floor plan, first floor master and screened in porch is waiting for you. The kitchen offers granite countertops with room for stools, SS appliances including refrigerator, gas stove and built in microwave. Living room is open to the second floor and had a gas fireplace. A dining area, Laundry area and half bath completes the first floor. Upstairs opens up to a large loft area, two additional bedrooms and a full bathroom. For your convenience you have a walk in attic space to store all your holiday boxes. HoA includes exterior maintenance, incl roof. No lawn mower needed here- that will be taken care of for you also by the HOA.but feel free to garden, or just sit it and chill on your back porch. Your new home is waiting for you !
